```

### Sound Engine (9 Layer + Reverb)

1. Sub-Boom: Noise Buffer, lowpass 85Hz, gain 2.8 → 0
1. Sub-Sine-Puls: Sine 22→48Hz, gain 1.1 → 0
1. Reactor-Hum: Sawtooth 38→125Hz, bandpass, gain 0→0.32→0
1. Growl: Square 48→92Hz, lowpass 380Hz
1. Sweep: Sine 180→5800Hz (das ikonische Whoop)
1. Harmonic Sweep: Sine 360→11600Hz
1. Power-Crack: Noise Buffer, highpass 800Hz
1. Clang: Square 380→28Hz
1. Running Hum: Sine 122Hz + Oberton 244Hz

- Cinematic Rumble: Noise lowpass 75Hz, peaking +16dB @ 42Hz
- Reverb: Convolver 3.5s decay
- Master DynamicsCompressor + Gain 1.6

